RPG Maker Plugins License Agreement

Copyright (c) 2024 moonyoulove

1. This license permits commercial use.
2. Users are not required to credit the original author in their work.
3. This content can be used for games of any genre.
4. Users are allowed to share this content with others without notifying the original author.
5. Users may modify and redistribute this content, but must adhere to the following conditions:
    5.1 Modified versions of the content cannot be sold separately, but can be included in games for sale.
    5.2 Modified content must include attribution to the original author (in any form or location).
